title: Look for Me audiobook by Lisa Gardner[EarReaders]
description:
Look for Me
Detective D. D. Warren, Book 9
By: Lisa Gardner
Narrated by: Regina Reagan
Length: 11 hrs and 26 mins
Unabridged
Release date: 02-15-18
Language: English
Publisher: Random House Audiobooks 


Random House presents the audiobook edition of Look for Me by Lisa Gardner, read by Regina Reagan.

Detective D. D. Warren and Flora Dane are in a race against time to save a young girl's life - or bring her to justice.

A family home has become a crime scene. Five people are involved: four of them have been savagely murdered; one - a 16-year-old girl - is missing.

Was she lucky to have escaped? Or is her absence evidence of something sinister?

Detective D. D. Warren is on the case, as is survivor-turned-avenger Flora Dane.

Seeking different types of justice, they must make sense of the clues left behind by a young woman who, as victim or suspect, is silently pleading, 'Look for me'.
